					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That will work as long as you have less than 256 bytes of metasprite data. When you have more, you're going to have to use some kind of indirect indexing, usually with <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">LDA &#40;foo&#41;,Y</tt> where foo is a pointer in the zeropage.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 85%; line-height: normal">Download STREEMERZ for NES from <a href="http://www.fauxgame.com" class="postlink">www.fauxgame.com</a>!</span></div>
